@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### LEARNING MODULE - Learning Management
### ============================================

### PATHS - List Learning Paths
GET {{baseUrl}}/learning/paths?page=1&limit=20&difficulty=intermediate
Authorization: {{token}}

### PATHS - Get Path Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/learning/paths/:pathId
Authorization: {{token}}

### PATHS - Create Path
POST {{baseUrl}}/learning/paths
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Advanced TypeScript Mastery",
  "description": "Master advanced TypeScript concepts and patterns",
  "difficulty": "advanced",
  "estimatedDuration": 40,
  "skills": ["typescript", "oop", "design-patterns"],
  "targetRole": "senior-developer"
}

### ENROLLMENTS - Enroll User
POST {{baseUrl}}/learning/enroll
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-uuid",
  "pathId": "path-uuid",
  "startDate": "2025-01-03"
}

### ENROLLMENTS - List Enrollments
GET {{baseUrl}}/learning/enrollments?userId=user-uuid
Authorization: {{token}}

### PROGRESS - Complete Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/learning/items/:itemId/complete
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 85,
  "timeSpent": 120,
  "notes": "Good understanding of concepts"
}

### SKILLS - List Available Skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/learning/skills?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: {{token}}

### SKILLS - Get My Skills
GET {{baseUrl}}/learning/my-skills
Authorization: {{token}}

### SKILLS - Assess Skill
POST {{baseUrl}}/learning/skills/:skillId/assess
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proficiencyLevel": "intermediate",
  "yearsOfExperience": 5,
  "assessmentScore": 75
}

### PLANS - Create Development Plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/learning/development-plans
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user-uuid",
  "title": "Frontend Development Roadmap",
  "targetSkills": ["react", "typescript", "testing"],
  "timeline": 6,
  "notes": "Personal development plan for Q1 2025"
}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Difficulties: beginner, intermediate, advanced, expert
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
